# 10. Customers Without Orders

```sql
SELECT c.*
FROM customers c
LEFT JOIN orders o
  ON c.customer_id = o.customer_id
WHERE o.customer_id IS NULL;
```

Alternative:

```sql
SELECT *
FROM customers c
WHERE NOT EXISTS (
    SELECT 1
    FROM orders o
    WHERE o.customer_id = c.customer_id
);
```

