# 11. Day-1 Retention

```sql
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT a.user_id)
FROM activity a
JOIN activity b
  ON a.user_id = b.user_id
 AND b.activity_date =
     DATE_ADD(a.activity_date, INTERVAL 1 DAY);
```

