# 12. Sessionization

### Previous Event

```sql
LAG(event_time) OVER(
    PARTITION BY user_id
    ORDER BY event_time
)
```

### New Session Flag

```sql
CASE
    WHEN prev_time IS NULL
      OR TIMESTAMPDIFF(
             MINUTE,
             prev_time,
             event_time
         ) > 30
    THEN 1
    ELSE 0
END
```

### Session Id

```sql
SUM(session_start) OVER(
    PARTITION BY user_id
    ORDER BY event_time
)
```

