# 13. Conditional Aggregation

```sql
SELECT
    COUNT(
        CASE
            WHEN status='Purchase'
            THEN 1
        END
    ) purchases
FROM events;
```

or

```sql
SELECT
    SUM(
        CASE
            WHEN status='Purchase'
            THEN 1
            ELSE 0
        END
    ) purchases
FROM events;
```

