# 17. Gap & Island Pattern

```sql
SELECT *,
       ROW_NUMBER() OVER(
           PARTITION BY user_id
           ORDER BY login_date
       ) rn
FROM logins;
```

Then:

```sql
DATE_SUB(
    login_date,
    INTERVAL rn DAY
)
```

Used for:

* Consecutive days
* Login streaks

