# 18. Common DATE Functions

Add Day

```sql
DATE_ADD(date_col, INTERVAL 1 DAY)
```

Subtract Day

```sql
DATE_SUB(date_col, INTERVAL 1 DAY)
```

Difference

```sql
DATEDIFF(date1, date2)
```

Timestamp Difference

```sql
TIMESTAMPDIFF(
    MINUTE,
    start_time,
    end_time
)
```

